#### Island Browser

#### Overview

This dashboard provides comprehensive visibility into user activity and account details within the Island Browser platform.

It includes control panel filters to refine the view by user source, type, and status. Metrics highlight the total number of users and active users for a quick overview of engagement. Pie charts break down users by source and type, while bar charts show user distribution by status and group memberships.

A line chart visualizes login activity over time, while tables highlight top email-verified users and provide essential user details for monitoring and auditing.
